  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2826590/extras/8a3a73d667a5336df37f3df405cc129d.avif?t=1742072001\" width=640 height=320 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sausage Cat is a relaxing puzzle game for cat lovers! This game is cozy, yet provides challenge for all ages. Help your sausage kittens get to their milk pots while filling all the room!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy diverse levels full of challenge and fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30 Levels </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Cozy and Pixelated Art-style</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Achievements for your account</p></li></ul>",
